  "decision_conditions": [
    "Planning permission was granted for single and two storey rear extensions under application P0599.10, which was implemented. According to the existing floor plans for P0599.10, the original dwelling had a gross internal floor space of 97 square metres, which fails to meet the standard of 120 square metres, thereby resulting in the unacceptable loss of small family homes within the Borough, contrary to Policy 8 of the Havering Local Plan.",
    "The intensification of the site would generate high levels of activity and result in an unacceptable impact on neighbouring residential occupiers in terms of noise and disturbance contrary to Policies 7 and 8 of the Havering Local Plan.",
    "In the absence of a legal agreement to prevent future occupants from applying for or obtaining a residents parking permit, the proposal fails to satisfactorily mitigate the parking impacts of the development, contrary to the provisions of Policy 24 of the Havering Local Plan (2016-2031) and Policy T6.1 of the London Plan.",
    "Statement Required by Article 35 (2) of the Town and Country Planning (Development Management Procedure) (England) Order 2015: Consideration was given to seeking amendments, but given conflict with adopted planning policy, notification of intended refusal and the reason(s) for it was given to Domenech Designs Limited via email on 3rd February 2022."
